                                <img src="assets/img/sustain-a-bowl/persona.png" class="img-fluid" alt="" data-action="zoom">
                            </figure>



                            <h3 class="mt-4">Journey map</h3>
                            <p>By examining the current state of Travis' lunch journey, we were able to identify pain points and opportunities for improvement:</p>

